b'KimiKiss Pure Rouge': b"Kouichi Sanada and Kazuki Aihara's childhood friend Mao Mizusawa has returned after living in France for a couple of years. The three friends help each other deal with the ups and downs of high school romance.\n\n(Source: ANN)"
